{"tid":631286,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【劫機畫面曝光】乘客鋼筆挾持國航空姐 大叫「保持5米，往後退」","createTime":"2018-04-16T10:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T01:29:06.000Z","uid":29627,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d41dba7e3ef07c7ec3923af10a1b5bc6f9eec2c8","tid":631286,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:28:37.000Z","msg":"【劫機畫面曝光】乘客鋼筆挾持國航空姐 大叫「保持5米，往後退」 <br />\n<br />\n 昨早由長沙飛往北京的國航CA1350航班，發生劫機事件，客機最後逼降在鄭州新鄭國際機場，劫機客被制服及拘捕，機艙乘客亦獲安全撤離。今日劫機一刻的短片曝光，在網上引發瘋傳。<br />\n<br />\n短片所見，徐姓男乘客以鋼筆挾持空姐，空姐嚇得癱軟坐在地上，有武警及談判人員上機艙與徐男談判，徐男大喊：「保持5米遠，不相干人等往後退」。在談判人員攻心未果情況下，3名便衣武警與1名公安民警分別從徐男正面和背後同時突擊把他制服，徐男被成功拘捕，空姐及所有乘客安全獲救。<br />\n<br />\n疑犯徐某41歲，事後當局稱他有精神病史。事發時突發精神病，用鋼筆做挾持工具。據悉，武警河南總隊出動90名兵力往鄭州機場戒備。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180416/large/1523860241_4d3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180416%2Flarge%2F1523860241_4d3c.jpg&h=c55eee10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180416/58079735\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180416%2F58079735&d=0955fzHkKFo8gU5cknr%2BF5nkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=bc183f37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180416%2F58079735&h=0cb1f3f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180416/58079735</a>"},{"pid":"84a620c61e3ebf29c8c72546fd39d189f296e57a","tid":631286,"uid":900,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T10:37:45.000Z","msg":"徐男被成功拘捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜撚野中文黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c7180e8736e994a3ea1343b1834361cd914b65","tid":631286,